    let needledata := and(mload(needleptr), mask)
    ptr := add(selfptr, sub(selflen, needlelen))
    loop:

    ptr := sub(ptr, 1)
    jumpi(loop, gt(add(ptr, 1), selfptr))
    ptr := selfptr
    jump(exit)
    ret:

    exit:
